   |INIVIDU-| Someone   |What person|That      |Each person| No one    |
   |  ALITY | Anyone    |Which thing|  person  |Everyone   | Nobody    |
   |        |           |Who  Which |That      | Cxiuj =   |           |
   |        |           |           |(specified) all,      |           |
   |        |           |           |  thing   | all the...|           |
